  "purpose": "Generate a single CLAUDE md project context file from all \n concept projections plus project level configuration \n Aggregates skill summaries , project structure , conventions , \n key files , and test commands into one markdown document \n for Claude Code sessions Closer to OpenApiTarget ( one \n file from all concepts ) than ClaudeSkillsTarget ( per concept \n files ) See Architecture doc Section 2.6"
